India has cleared the use of two new vaccines - Corbevax and Covovax.
Corbevax is a protein subunit vaccine made by Hyderabad-based company biological-E.
Covovax is a nanoparticle vaccine being manufactured by Pune-based Serum Institute which is also manufacturing Covishield.
